        <p>The Counterfactual track checks whether the decision follows from valid evidence.</p>
        <span class="related-link">Read &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.22737" class="related-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="related-tag">Paper</div>
        <h3>GroundEval: Deterministic Agent Evaluation</h3>
        <p>The full paper with formal properties, all three tracks, and case studies.</p>
